Why don't we have a seat and talk it over.

700
00:54:00,740 --> 00:54:03,740
布魯斯，你有紙和筆嗎？
Do you have a piece of paper and a pencil?

701
00:54:15,041 --> 00:54:16,340
謝謝
Thanks.

702
00:54:17,042 --> 00:54:18,041
那麼
So...

703
00:54:19,842 --> 00:54:21,641
迪格斯先生
Mister Dekins...

704
00:54:22,441 --> 00:54:24,740
接著安迪問迪格斯
And then Andy says, " Mr. Dekins...

705
00:54:24,742 --> 00:54:27,941
你想讓你的兒子去哈佛還是耶魯？
...do you want your sons to go to Harvard or Yale?"

706
00:54:27,942 --> 00:54:29,041
他沒有這樣說
He didn't say that!

707
00:54:29,343 --> 00:54:31,842
上帝可以作證
As God as my witness!

708
00:54:32,143 --> 00:54:34,042
迪格斯愣了一會兒
Dekins blinked for a second...

709
00:54:34,043 --> 00:54:37,143
傻笑著和安迪握手
...then he laughed and actually shook Andy's hand.

710
00:54:37,644 --> 00:54:39,843
老天！和他握手
- My ass! - Shook his hand.

711
00:54:40,143 --> 00:54:43,242
我告訴你們，我感到……
I tell you, I near soiled myself!

712
00:54:43,243 --> 00:54:47,243
安迪若穿上那套衣服
All he needed was a suit and tie and a jiggly hula gal on his desk...

713
00:54:47,744 --> 00:54:50,243
他就會變成德福瑞恩先生的了
...he'd have been "Mr. Dufresne," if you please.

714
00:54:50,545 --> 00:54:52,144
安迪，又交上新朋友了？
Making a few friends?

715
00:54:53,445 --> 00:54:55,344
我不認為是朋友
I wouldn't say "friends."

716
00:54:55,345 --> 00:54:59,344
我是一個能提供準確財政計劃的謀殺犯
I'm a convicted murderer who provides sound financial planning.

717
00:54:59,345 --> 00:55:01,844
只是某人不錯的僕人
It's a wonderful pet to have.

718
00:55:01,846 --> 00:55:03,645
至少可以令你離開洗衣房
Got you out of the laundry, though.

719
00:55:03,946 --> 00:55:06,045
可能不是那麼簡單的
It might do more than that.

720
00:55:06,046 --> 00:55:08,945
我打算擴大圖書館，找點新書
How about expanding the library. Get some new books.

721
00:55:08,946 --> 00:55:11,545
還是找張檯球桌吧
If you ask for something, ask for a pool table.

722
00:55:13,247 --> 00:55:16,446
你打算怎麼做，我是說
How do you expect to do that? I mean...

723
00:55:16,447 --> 00:55:19,447
怎麼得到新書，向誰請求
...get new books in here, "Mr. Dufresne, if you please."

724
00:55:19,947 --> 00:55:21,946
我會向典獄長要錢
I'll ask the warden for funds.

725
00:55:22,848 --> 00:55:27,347
噢，孩子，孩子，我經歷了六個典獄長，懂得了一條
Six wardens have been through here in my tenure, and I've learned...

726
00:55:27,348 --> 00:55:29,847
一個事實，宇宙真理
...one immutable, universal truth:

727
00:55:29,848 --> 00:55:31,447
那個人還沒有生出來
Not one born whose asshole...

728
00:55:31,449 --> 00:55:36,448
你向他們提出定遭拒絕的
...wouldn't pucker up tighter than a snare drum when you ask for funds.

729
00:55:37,249 --> 00:55:40,349
-預算不夠用 -我知道
- The budget's stretched thin as it is. - I see.

730
00:55:40,449 --> 00:55:44,089
或許我寫信向參議員提出
Maybe I could write the state senate and request funds from them.

731
00:55:44,129 --> 00:55:48,129
只有三種情況能動納稅人的錢
They have only three ways to spend the taxpayers' money for prisons:

732
00:55:48,450 --> 00:55:51,009
多建圍牆、多建牢房和增加監獄
More walls, more bars, more guards.

733
00:55:51,050 --> 00:55:53,889
若你批准，我想嘗試一下，每週一封信
I'd like to try, with permission. A letter a week.

734
00:55:53,930 --> 00:55:56,649
-他們不能永不理會 -當然能夠
- They can't ignore me forever. - Sure can.

735
00:55:56,930 --> 00:55:59,649
如果你寫著高興那就寫吧
But you write your letters if it makes you happy.

736
00:55:59,931 --> 00:56:02,530
我來替你寄出，怎樣？
I'll even mail them for you. How's that?

737
00:56:04,132 --> 00:56:07,092
就這樣，安迪開始每周寫一封信
So Andy started writing a letter a week...

738
00:56:07,132 --> 00:56:08,731
就像他說得那樣
... just like he said.

739
00:56:12,932 --> 00:56:15,691
但如諾頓所說
And like Norton said...

740
00:56:15,733 --> 00:56:17,252
一直都無回覆
... Andy got no answers.

741
00:56:25,453 --> 00:56:30,332
過了四月，安迪已幫半數獄警們報稅
The following April, he did tax returns for half the guards at Shawshank.

742
00:56:32,184 --> 00:56:34,153
後來，全都找他幫忙了
Year after that, he did them all...

743
00:56:34,154 --> 00:56:36,083
連典獄長納稅務都由他處理
... including the warden's.

744
00:56:37,824 --> 00:56:41,464
後來，他們安排
Year after that, they rescheduled the intramural season...

745
00:56:41,506 --> 00:56:43,905
球隊在稅季中比賽
... to coincide with tax season.

746
00:56:45,506 --> 00:56:50,185
所有的球隊都帶著報稅表
The guards on the opposing teams all remembered to bring their W-2s.

747
00:56:49,825 --> 00:56:51,264
所以莫爾斯比監獄……
So Moresby Prison...

748
00:56:51,306 --> 00:56:53,785
配給你一支槍，但要你自己付錢
...issued you a gun, but you paid for it.

749
00:56:53,826 --> 00:56:55,665
對，連手槍皮套也是
Right. The holster too.

750
00:56:55,706 --> 00:56:58,385
那可以減免稅款，你可把它記下來
That's tax-deductible. You can write that off.

751
00:56:58,426 --> 00:57:01,426
是的！安迪就像一個正常的會計師
Yes, sir! Andy was a regular cottage industry.

752
00:57:02,107 --> 00:57:06,626
事實上，在稅季中他如此的忙，允許有一個幫手
In fact, it got so busy at tax time, he was allowed a staff.

753
00:57:06,907 --> 00:57:09,586
瑞德，你可以取1040號表格來嗎？
Could you hand me a stack of 1040s?

754
00:57:09,628 --> 00:57:14,427
每年有一個月離開監獄去木工場做工
Got me out of the wood shop a month out of the year, and that was fine by me.

755
00:57:15,628 --> 00:57:18,828
同時，安迪仍舊不斷的寫信
And still, he kept sending those letters.

756
00:57:25,630 --> 00:57:26,629
安迪、瑞德，布魯斯出事了
It's Brooks.

757
00:57:27,709 --> 00:57:29,228
看著門
Watch the door.

758
00:57:29,510 --> 00:57:30,829
冷靜點，布魯斯
Please, Brooks.

759
00:57:31,109 --> 00:57:32,908
千萬別衝動，放下來！
- Calm the fuck down. - Stay back!

760
00:57:33,310 --> 00:57:35,909
-放下來，該死！ -發生什麼事？
- Stay back, goddamn it! - What's going on?

761
00:57:36,230 --> 00:57:38,869
他突然掏出刀來
One second he's fine, then out come the knives.

762
00:57:38,911 --> 00:57:40,710
有事慢慢商量好嗎？
We can talk about this, right?

763
00:57:41,031 --> 00:57:44,711
沒商量餘地的，我要割斷他的喉嚨
There's nothing to talk about. I'll cut his fucking throat.

764
00:57:45,031 --> 00:57:46,870
他有什麼對不起你？
What's he done to you?

765
00:57:46,912 --> 00:57:48,631
去問獄警吧
It's what they done!

766
00:57:49,111 --> 00:57:50,430
我別無選擇
I got no choice.

767
00:57:50,832 --> 00:57:53,271
我們都知道，你不會傷害海伍德的
You won't hurt Heywood. We all know that.

768
00:57:53,312 --> 00:57:55,991
-對嗎，海伍德？ -是的
- Right, Heywood? - Sure.

769
00:57:56,032 --> 00:57:59,592
他是你的朋友，布魯斯是講道理的
He's a friend of yours, and Brooks is a reasonable man.

770
00:57:59,633 --> 00:58:00,712
對嗎？
Right, guys?

771
00:58:01,713 --> 00:58:04,232
那麼把刀放下，看著我
So put the knife down. Look at me.

772
00:58:04,513 --> 00:58:06,712
把刀放下
Put the knife down.

773
00:58:08,633 --> 00:58:10,712
看看他的脖子
Look at his neck, for God's sake.

774
00:58:11,514 --> 00:58:13,833
看看他的脖子，他在流血
Look at his neck. He's bleeding.

775
00:58:14,714 --> 00:58:16,393
這是唯一
It's the only way...

776
00:58:16,434 --> 00:58:18,433
使我留在這堛瑪鴘k
...they'd let me stay.

777
00:58:18,714 --> 00:58:21,273
你瘋了，你不會這樣做的
This is crazy. You don't want to do this.

778
00:58:21,314 --> 00:58:23,433
放下，放下刀
Put it, put it down.

779
00:58:32,116 --> 00:58:33,575
放鬆
Take it easy.

780
00:58:34,316 --> 00:58:35,915
一切都會好的
You'll be all right.

781
00:58:36,916 --> 00:58:38,675
他？那麼我呢？
Him? What about me?

782
00:58:38,716 --> 00:58:41,275
這個愚蠢的瘋子差點割斷我的喉嚨
Crazy old fool damn near cut my throat!

783
00:58:41,316 --> 00:58:43,395
你就連刮鬍子也比這刮得厲害
You've had worse from shaving.

784
00:58:43,437 --> 00:58:45,676
究竟怎麼會這樣？
What did you do to set him off?

785
00:58:45,717 --> 00:58:48,036
沒什麼，我只是進來和他道別
Nothing. I come in here to say farewell.

786
00:58:48,638 --> 00:58:51,237
難到你沒聽說？他獲得假釋
Ain't you heard? His parole's come through.

787
00:58:53,637 --> 00:58:56,597
我就是不明白，發生什麼了
I just don't understand what happened in there.

788
00:58:56,638 --> 00:58:59,598
老傢伙瘋了
Old man's crazy as a rat in a tin shithouse.

789
00:58:59,638 --> 00:59:01,677
夠了
That's enough out of you.

790
00:59:01,718 --> 00:59:04,437
-我聽說你嚇得尿流 -去你媽的
- Heard he had you shitting your pants. - Fuck you.

791
00:59:04,719 --> 00:59:05,918
不要說了！
IKnock it off.

792
00:59:06,839 --> 00:59:08,318
布魯斯不是瘋了
Brooks ain't no bug.

793
00:59:12,120 --> 00:59:13,919
他只是被體制化了
He's just institutionalized.

794
00:59:15,320 --> 00:59:17,399
體制化？什麼東西？
"Institutionalized," my ass.

795
00:59:17,440 --> 00:59:21,440
他在此已有五十年了，海伍德，五十年！
The man's been in here 50 years, Heywood, 50 years!

796
00:59:21,641 --> 00:59:23,480
這是他唯一認識的地方
This is all he knows.

797
00:59:23,520 --> 00:59:25,999
在這兒，他是個重要的人
In here, he's an important man...

798
00:59:26,041 --> 00:59:27,120
一個有教養的人
...an educated man.

799
00:59:27,921 --> 00:59:29,920
在外面，他什麼都不是
Outside, he's nothing.

800
00:59:30,721 --> 00:59:32,400
只是一個假釋出來的囚犯
Just a used-up con with arthritis in both hands.

801
00:59:33,442 --> 00:59:37,442
申請張借書證都有困難
Probably couldn't get a library card if he tried.

802
00:59:37,722 --> 00:59:39,441
你明白我說的話嗎？
You know what I'm trying to say?

803
00:59:39,722 --> 00:59:42,641
瑞德，我相信你說是屁話
I do believe you're talking out of your ass.

804
00:59:43,922 --> 00:59:46,121
怎麼想隨你吧
You believe whatever you want.

805
00:59:46,723 --> 00:59:49,122
我告訴你，這些圍牆很有趣的
But I tell you these walls are funny.

806
00:59:50,724 --> 00:59:52,443
開始，你恨它們
First you hate them.

807
00:59:54,244 --> 00:59:56,123
接著，你適應了它們
Then you get used to them.

808
00:59:58,124 --> 01:00:00,123
時間久了
Enough time passes...

809
01:00:00,724 --> 01:00:02,723
你開始離不開它們
...you get so you depend on them.

810
01:00:03,724 --> 01:00:06,083
那就是被體制化了
That's "institutionalized."

811
01:00:06,125 --> 01:00:07,604
Shit.

812
01:00:07,644 --> 01:00:10,443
-我永遠不會那樣的 -對嗎？
- I could never get like that. - Oh, yeah?

813
01:00:11,326 --> 01:00:14,005
因為你沒布魯斯那樣長時間在此
Wait till you've been here as long as Brooks.

814
01:00:14,045 --> 01:00:15,644
太對了
Goddamn right.

815
01:00:18,246 --> 01:00:20,125
他們把你送到這堥茈肮
They send you here for life...

816
01:00:20,846 --> 01:00:23,125
這就是他們確實想要做的
...that's exactly what they take.

817
01:00:24,846 --> 01:00:26,805
無論怎樣已經部分達到了
Part that counts, anyway.

818
01:00:34,947 --> 01:00:37,846
我不能再照顧你了，傑克
I can't take care of you no more, Jake.

819
01:00:39,028 --> 01:00:40,747
你走吧
You go on now.

820
01:00:41,948 --> 01:00:43,427
你自由了
You're free.

821
01:00:44,749 --> 01:00:46,348
你自由了
You're free.

822
01:01:05,351 --> 01:01:07,030
布魯斯，祝你好運
Good luck, Brooksie.

823
01:01:44,954 --> 01:01:46,433
大家好
Dear fellas:

824
01:01:46,755 --> 01:01:50,755
外面的改變令我難以想像
I can't believe how fast things move on the outside.

825
01:01:52,234 --> 01:01:54,953
老頭，找死啊？
Watch it, old-timer! Want to get killed?

826
01:01:56,155 --> 01:01:59,635
我童年時只見過一次汽車
I saw an automobile once when I was a kid...

827
01:02:00,355 --> 01:02:02,754
但現在到處都是
... but now they're everywhere.

828
01:02:06,436 --> 01:02:10,755
世界在一片巨大的忙碌之中
The world went and got itself in a big damn hurry.

829
01:02:26,558 --> 01:02:30,238
假釋委員會給我安排了中途宿舍
The parole board got me into this halfway house...

830
01:02:30,638 --> 01:02:32,397
叫做「釀酒人」
... called "The Brewer"...

831
01:02:32,438 --> 01:02:33,797
和一份工作
... and a job...

832
01:02:33,839 --> 01:02:36,839
在一家雜貨店堨]裝食物
... bagging groceries at the Food-Way.

833
01:02:38,359 --> 01:02:40,918
雖然很辛苦，但我很努力工作
It's hard work and I try to keep up...

834
01:02:40,959 --> 01:02:43,358
我的手經常感到酸痛
... but my hands hurt most of the time.

835
01:02:43,640 --> 01:02:45,799
記得用兩層袋
Make sure your man double-bags.

836
01:02:45,840 --> 01:02:47,839
上次幾乎穿底了
Last time, the bottom near came out.

837
01:02:48,561 --> 01:02:51,601
聽到那女士說的嗎？
Make sure you double-bag like the lady says. Understand?

838
01:02:51,641 --> 01:02:53,200
是的，先生
Yes, sir. Surely will.

839
01:02:53,240 --> 01:02:56,760
我想那店主不太喜歡我
I don't think the store manager likes me very much.

840
01:02:59,761 --> 01:03:04,040
有時工作完後，我到公園堨h餵那些鴿子
Sometimes after work, I go to the park and feed the birds.

841
01:03:04,562 --> 01:03:05,961
我一直希望
I keep thinking...

842
01:03:06,241 --> 01:03:09,561
傑克會飛來和我打招呼
... Jake might just show up and say hello.

843
01:03:10,162 --> 01:03:12,161
但它從未來過
But he never does.

844
01:03:13,363 --> 01:03:18,242
我希望，不管在哪，它都過的很好，又交到新朋友
I hope, wherever he is, he's doing okay and making new friends.

845
01:03:21,843 --> 01:03:24,562
晚上我不能入睡
I have trouble sleeping at night.

846
01:03:24,844 --> 01:03:28,164
經常作惡夢，身體像一直往下掉
I have bad dreams like I'm falling.

847
01:03:28,444 --> 01:03:30,803
醒來時感到恐懼
I wake up scared.

848
01:03:30,844 --> 01:03:34,963
要想一會兒才知道自己在哪兒
Sometimes it takes me a while to remember where I am.

849
01:03:36,565 --> 01:03:41,564
也許我該用槍打劫，讓他們好送我回家
Maybe I should get a gun and rob the Food-Way so they'd send me home.

850
01:03:41,846 --> 01:03:46,165
我可以打死那個店主，當作額外補助
I could shoot the manager while I was at it. Sort of like a bonus.

851
01:03:47,846 --> 01:03:51,846
但我已經太老了，再也幹不了這種蠢事
I guess I'm too old for that sort of nonsense anymore.

852
01:03:52,046 --> 01:03:53,925
我不喜歡這地方
I don't like it here.

853
01:03:53,967 --> 01:03:57,967
它令我感到害怕，我決定……
I'm tired of being afraid all the time. I've decided...

854
01:03:58,846 --> 01:04:00,445
離開
... not to stay.

855
01:04:11,448 --> 01:04:14,127
我懷疑他們會爭論
I doubt they'll kick up any fuss...

856
01:04:14,168 --> 01:04:17,648
但不是為我這個老壞蛋
... not for an old crook like me.

857
01:05:04,649 --> 01:05:08,517
「老布來此一遊」

858
01:05:19,975 --> 01:05:24,254
我懷疑他們會爭論，但不是為我這種老壞蛋
"I doubt they'll kick up any fuss, not for an old crook like me.

859
01:05:25,255 --> 01:05:29,215
另外，跟海伍德說，上次的事很對不起，別放在心上
P.S. Tell Heywood I'm sorry I put a knife to his throat.

860
01:05:29,255 --> 01:05:31,654
不再有痛苦的感覺了，布魯斯
No hard feelings. Brooks."

861
01:05:42,056 --> 01:05:44,055
他應該死在這兒
He should have died in here.

862
01:05:49,578 --> 01:05:50,977
你該死的做了什麼？
What the fuck have you done?

863
01:05:51,257 --> 01:05:53,856
一團糟，我來告訴你
It's a goddamn mess, I'll tell you that.

864
01:05:59,458 --> 01:06:03,178
-這些都是什麼？ -你告訴我，全都寄給你的
- What's all this? - You tell me. They're addressed to you.

865
01:06:04,459 --> 01:06:05,778
拿著
Take it.

