"Dear Mr. Dufresne:

867
01:06:16,980 --> 01:06:19,019
應你的來信請求，州政府撥給……
In response to your inquiries...

868
01:06:19,110 --> 01:06:23,389
你的圖書館計劃經費
...the state has allocated the enclosed funds for your library project."

869
01:06:24,180 --> 01:06:26,139
這是200元
This is $ 200.

870
01:06:26,181 --> 01:06:30,131
而州立圖書館
"In addition, the library district has generously responded...

871
01:06:30,374 --> 01:06:32,933
捐出舊書和日常用品
...with a donation of used books and sundries.

872
01:06:33,143 --> 01:06:37,271
這些應是你所需要的，而此事亦告一段落
We trust this will fill your needs. We now consider the matter closed.

873
01:06:37,481 --> 01:06:39,277
懇請閣下勿再來信
Please stop sending us letters."

874
01:06:39,515 --> 01:06:42,178
典獄長回來前要清理好
Clear all this out before the warden gets back.

875
01:06:42,419 --> 01:06:43,579
知道
Yes, sir.

876
01:06:47,858 --> 01:06:49,018
安迪，真不錯
Good for you, Andy.

877
01:06:51,997 --> 01:06:53,121
哦！
Wow!

878
01:06:54,333 --> 01:06:56,265
只用了六年時間
It only took six years.

879
01:06:57,836 --> 01:07:00,565
由現在起，我每星期寫兩封信
From now on, I'll write two letters a week instead of one.

880
01:07:00,773 --> 01:07:04,106
你真的很瘋狂，把這兒清理乾淨
I believe you're crazy enough. Get this stuff out...

881
01:07:04,376 --> 01:07:05,205
照他說的辦
...like he said.

882
01:07:05,411 --> 01:07:06,810
我去廁所
I've got to pinch a loaf.

883
01:07:07,013 --> 01:07:08,478
回來時
When I come back...

884
01:07:08,681 --> 01:07:10,444
不想見到這些書
...this is all gone, all right?

885
01:07:59,205 --> 01:08:00,602
安迪，聽到了嗎？
Do you hear that?

886
01:09:09,346 --> 01:09:10,506
德弗瑞恩！
Dufresne!

887
01:09:13,049 --> 01:09:14,573
安迪，讓我出去
Andy, let me out!

888
01:09:17,635 --> 01:09:18,499
安迪

889
01:09:21,459 --> 01:09:26,396
我到今天也沒不明白，這兩個意大利女人在唱著什麼
I have no idea to this day what those two Italian ladies were singing about.

890
01:09:26,700 --> 01:09:28,928
事實上，我也不想去明白
Truth is, I don't want to know.

891
01:09:29,134 --> 01:09:31,624
有些東西不說更好
Some things are best left unsaid.

892
01:09:35,210 --> 01:09:37,938
我想那是，如此的美
I like to think it was something so beautiful...

893
01:09:38,144 --> 01:09:40,272
無法用語言來形容
... it can't be expressed in words...

894
01:09:40,483 --> 01:09:43,381
美得讓你心痛
... and makes your heart ache because of it.

895
01:09:45,051 --> 01:09:47,541
我告訴你，那聲音飛翔
I tell you, those voices soared...

896
01:09:47,823 --> 01:09:52,122
比在這個灰暗地方的任何一個人夢想的都要高遠
... higher and farther than anybody in a gray place dares to dream.

897
01:09:52,329 --> 01:09:55,695
像一隻美麗的小鳥，飛進了我們這灰色的鳥籠
It was like a beautiful bird flapped into our drab cage...

898
01:09:55,899 --> 01:09:58,662
讓這些圍牆消失了
... and made those walls dissolve away.

899
01:09:59,101 --> 01:10:01,296
在那一刻
And for the briefest of moments...

900
01:10:01,503 --> 01:10:04,495
每個在肖申克的落伍者，感到了的自由
... every last man at Shawshank felt free.

901
01:10:07,076 --> 01:10:09,739
但那令典獄長極度憤怒
It pissed the warden off something awful.

902
01:10:11,048 --> 01:10:12,035
開門
Open the door.

903
01:10:14,951 --> 01:10:16,713
開門！
Open it up!

904
01:10:18,022 --> 01:10:20,749
德弗瑞恩，開門
Dufresne, open this door!

905
01:10:22,094 --> 01:10:23,286
把它關掉！
Turn that off!

906
01:10:30,375 --> 01:10:32,624
我警告你，德弗瑞恩！把它關掉
I am warning you. Turn that off!

907
01:10:46,236 --> 01:10:47,235
德弗瑞恩

908
01:10:50,668 --> 01:10:52,158
你落到我手堣F
You're mine now.

909
01:10:59,279 --> 01:11:02,477
安迪被關禁閉兩周
Andy got two weeks in the hole for that little stunt.

910
01:11:02,577 --> 01:11:04,135
站起來
On your feet.

911
01:11:05,982 --> 01:11:07,648
-看看誰回來了 -大藝術家！
- Hey, look who's here. - Maestro!

912
01:11:09,982 --> 01:11:13,611
你就不能放些好聽的嗎，嗯？比如漢克.威廉姆斯！
You couldn't play something good, huh? Like Hank Williams?

913
01:11:13,822 --> 01:11:16,586
還沒來得及接受點播，他們就破門進來了
They broke the door down before I could take requests.

914
01:11:16,702 --> 01:11:19,796
-被關了兩周，值得嗎？ -那是我最好的時光
- Was it worth two weeks? - Easiest time I ever did.

915
01:11:20,402 --> 01:11:24,566
沒有被關小號容易過的事，那個地方一個星期就像一年
- No such thing as easy time in the hole. - A week in the hole is like a year.

916
01:11:24,626 --> 01:11:27,891
對，我有莫扎特先生陪我
- Damn straight. - I had Mr. Mozart to keep me company.

917
01:11:27,986 --> 01:11:30,921
他們讓你帶留聲機到那兒？
So they let you tote that record player down there, huh?

918
01:11:33,870 --> 01:11:35,201
它就在這兒
It was in here.

919
01:11:35,982 --> 01:11:37,176
在這兒
In here.

920
01:11:38,254 --> 01:11:40,313
這就是音樂的魅力，他們……
That's the beauty of music. They...

921
01:11:40,462 --> 01:11:42,760
不能把它從你這兒奪走
...can't get that from you.

922
01:11:46,094 --> 01:11:48,426
你們從沒此感覺嗎？
Haven't you ever felt that way about music?

923
01:11:50,094 --> 01:11:53,188
我年輕時曾學過吹口琴
Well, I played a mean harmonica as a younger man.

924
01:11:54,094 --> 01:11:55,755
可是，現在已經失去興趣了
Lost interest in it, though.

925
01:11:55,918 --> 01:11:57,476
因為在這堥S有任何意義
Didn't make much sense in here.

926
01:11:57,774 --> 01:11:59,742
這堣~是它最有意義的地方
Here's where it makes the most sense.

927
01:12:00,205 --> 01:12:02,230
你需要它就不會忘記它
You need it so you don't forget.

928
01:12:02,734 --> 01:12:03,894
忘記？
Forget?

929
01:12:04,238 --> 01:12:07,298
忘記有一些
Forget that there are...

930
01:12:07,406 --> 01:12:08,805
地方
...places...

931
01:12:10,762 --> 01:12:14,562
在這個世界上，不是用石頭圍成
...in the world that aren't made out of stone.

932
01:12:15,592 --> 01:12:17,059
有些東西……
There's something...

933
01:12:17,618 --> 01:12:18,983
在內心……
...inside...

934
01:12:19,218 --> 01:12:21,152
不能到達……
...that they can't get to...

935
01:12:21,298 --> 01:12:22,629
……不能觸摸
...that they can't touch.

936
01:12:23,122 --> 01:12:24,521
屬於你
That's yours.

937
01:12:25,970 --> 01:12:27,528
你在說什麼？
What are you talking about?

938
01:12:28,773 --> 01:12:29,967
希望
Hope.

939
01:12:30,981 --> 01:12:32,278
希望
Hope.

940
01:12:34,116 --> 01:12:36,084
我告訴你，我的朋友
Let me tell you something, my friend.

941
01:12:36,805 --> 01:12:39,069
希望是很危險的東西
Hope is a dangerous thing.

942
01:12:40,617 --> 01:12:43,313
希望會讓人瘋狂
Hope can drive a man insane.

943
01:12:43,688 --> 01:12:45,781
它在這兒沒用
It's got no use on the inside.

944
01:12:45,928 --> 01:12:48,089
你最好習慣這想法
You'd better get used to that idea.

945
01:12:50,439 --> 01:12:51,906
就像布魯斯？
Like Brooks did?

946
01:13:17,387 --> 01:13:18,354
坐下
Sit down.

947
01:13:23,467 --> 01:13:26,732
你因終身監禁在此三十年
Says here that you've served 30 years of a life sentence.

948
01:13:28,198 --> 01:13:30,223
覺得自己被改造了嗎？
You feel you've been rehabilitated?

949
01:13:30,374 --> 01:13:31,568
是的，先生
Oh, yes, sir.

950
01:13:32,775 --> 01:13:34,072
毫無疑問
Without a doubt.

951
01:13:35,474 --> 01:13:37,840
老實說我己改過
I can honestly say I'm a changed man.

952
01:13:39,699 --> 01:13:41,599
我已不會危害社會
No danger to society here.

953
01:13:42,367 --> 01:13:43,857
上帝可以作證
God's honest truth.

954
01:13:46,303 --> 01:13:48,362
真的改變了
Absolutely rehabilitated.

955
01:13:53,303 --> 01:13:54,362
「不合格」

956
01:13:58,545 --> 01:13:59,842
三十年
Thirty years.

957
01:14:01,849 --> 01:14:03,714
當你這樣說時
Jesus, when you say it like that...

958
01:14:04,504 --> 01:14:06,233
想過是怎樣過的嗎？
You wonder where it went.

959
01:14:08,569 --> 01:14:10,662
我在想十年是怎樣過去的
I wonder where 10 years went.

960
01:14:15,416 --> 01:14:16,383
這兒
Here.

961
01:14:17,523 --> 01:14:20,185
這是慶祝你假釋被拒絕的禮物
A little parole rejection present.

962
01:14:21,467 --> 01:14:23,094
打來看看吧
Go ahead and open it.

963
01:14:24,270 --> 01:14:26,238
跟你的競爭對手買的
Went through one of your competitors.

964
01:14:26,506 --> 01:14:29,566
別介意，我想讓它給你一個驚喜
I hope you don't mind. I wanted it to be a surprise.

965
01:14:39,685 --> 01:14:41,118
它真漂亮
It's very pretty.

966
01:14:42,890 --> 01:14:44,016
謝謝你
Thank you.

967
01:14:46,659 --> 01:14:48,092
你會用它來吹奏嗎？
You going to play it?

968
01:14:52,698 --> 01:14:53,892
不
No.

969
01:14:57,570 --> 01:14:58,935
不會是現在
Not right now.

970
01:15:16,657 --> 01:15:17,681
關上！
Roll in!

971
01:15:33,657 --> 01:15:35,681
「這個新女孩給你紀念十週年，安迪」

972
01:15:53,961 --> 01:15:55,121
熄燈
Lights out!

973
01:16:29,796 --> 01:16:31,922
安迪說到做到……
Andy was as good as his word.

974
01:16:32,298 --> 01:16:35,063
他每周寫兩封信
He wrote two letters a week instead of one.

975
01:16:37,136 --> 01:16:41,233
1959年，州議員最後終於面對現實
In 1959, the state senate finally clued in to the fact...

976
01:16:41,475 --> 01:16:44,603
那200元的支票起不了作用
... they couldn't buy him off with just a $ 200 check.

977
01:16:44,810 --> 01:16:49,110
最後通過每年撥款500元
Appropriations Committee voted an annual payment of $500...

978
01:16:49,314 --> 01:16:51,216
來讓他閉嘴
... just to shut him up.

979
01:16:51,417 --> 01:16:54,409
隨後安迪所說的令你感到更意外
And you'd be amazed how far Andy could stretch it.

980
01:16:54,621 --> 01:16:57,555
他跟讀書會和慈善機構談至
He made deals with book clubs, charity groups.

981
01:16:57,756 --> 01:17:00,521
他用剩下來的錢來買書
He bought remaindered books by the pound...

982
01:17:01,028 --> 01:17:02,551
《金銀島》
Treasure Island.

983
01:17:03,096 --> 01:17:04,426
羅伯特·路易斯……
Robert Louis...

984
01:17:04,631 --> 01:17:05,654
斯蒂文森
Stevenson.

985
01:17:05,865 --> 01:17:07,230
科幻類，冒險類
Fiction, adventure.

986
01:17:09,802 --> 01:17:10,827
下一本是什麼？
What's next?

987
01:17:11,038 --> 01:17:14,097
是汽車修理
I got here Auto Repair...

988
01:17:14,841 --> 01:17:16,001
和肥皂雕刻技術
...and Soap Carving.

989
01:17:16,208 --> 01:17:19,439
技術與愛好，教育性那一欄
Trade skills and hobbies. Under "Educational," behind you.

990
01:17:19,645 --> 01:17:21,511
《基督山伯爵》
Count of Monte Crisco.

991
01:17:21,981 --> 01:17:24,279
那書不值一看
That's "Cristo," you dumb shit.

992
01:17:24,835 --> 01:17:25,823
作者是亞歷山大……
By Alexandree...

993
01:17:26,303 --> 01:17:27,564
……什麼……馬
...Dum-ass.

994
01:17:28,304 --> 01:17:29,329
「草泥馬」
Dumb ass.

995
01:17:31,642 --> 01:17:32,700
「草泥馬」？
Dumb ass?

996
01:17:35,611 --> 01:17:37,579
是大仲馬。德弗瑞恩，知道那是什麼故事嗎？
Dumas. IKnow what that's about?

997
01:17:39,849 --> 01:17:41,817
講越獄的，你喜歡看的
You'd like it. It's about a prison break.

998
01:17:42,018 --> 01:17:45,920
那我覺得應該發到「教育類」，對吧？
We ought to file that under "Educational" too, oughtn't we?

999
01:17:46,789 --> 01:17:50,886
我們其餘的隨時盡可能幫忙
The rest of us did our best to pitch in when and where we could.

1000
01:17:51,460 --> 01:17:53,223
到了肯尼迪遇刺那一年
By the year Kennedy was shot...

1001
01:17:53,463 --> 01:17:57,956
安迪把一個充滿松脂味的儲藏間
... Andy had transformed a storage room smelling of turpentine...

1002
01:17:58,267 --> 01:18:01,361
變成了新英格蘭州最好的的監獄圖書館
... into the best prison library in New England...

1003
01:18:02,071 --> 01:18:05,007
那埵陶怞n的漢克威廉姆斯唱片集
... complete with a fine selection of Hank Williams.

1004
01:18:12,382 --> 01:18:14,316
那也是諾頓典獄長髮展大計的一年
That was also when Warden Norton...

1005
01:18:14,517 --> 01:18:17,453
推廣他著名的「內在改造」計劃
... instituted his famous "Inside Out" program.

1006
01:18:17,920 --> 01:18:19,980
你可能從報紙上讀到過
You may remember reading about it.

1007
01:18:20,223 --> 01:18:23,317
所有的媒體都刊出他的照片
It made the papers and got his picture in Look magazine.

1008
01:18:23,526 --> 01:18:24,824
這不是放任的方式
It's no free ride...

1009
01:18:25,027 --> 01:18:28,258
……而是一種真正的進步
...but rather a genuine progressive advance...

1010
01:18:28,464 --> 01:18:30,955
……讓犯人恢復道德
...in corrections and rehabilitation.

1011
01:18:31,300 --> 01:18:33,825
收容人被適當的監督
Our inmates, properly supervised...

1012
01:18:34,036 --> 01:18:36,664
使他們能在外面工作
...will be put to work outside these walls...

1013
01:18:36,874 --> 01:18:39,834
為大眾服務
...performing all manner of public service.

1014
01:18:40,110 --> 01:18:42,341
他們會懂得勞動的價值
These men can learn the value...

1015
01:18:42,546 --> 01:18:46,346
為社會服務的誠實勞動
...of an honest day's labor and provide a service to the community...

1016
01:18:46,550 --> 01:18:51,248
在最低耗支情況下，來利用納稅人的金錢
...at a bare minimum of expense to Mr. And Mrs. John Q. Taxpayer.

1017
01:18:51,989 --> 01:18:54,320
當然，諾頓沒有跟報界說
Of course he didn't tell the press...

1018
01:18:54,525 --> 01:18:57,982
「最低耗支」其實是相當不確切的說法
... that "bare minimum of expense" is a fairly loose term.

1019
01:18:58,295 --> 01:19:01,321
有很多辦法能瞞天過海的
There are 100 different ways to skim off the top.

1020
01:19:01,531 --> 01:19:04,022
人力，物力，你說多少就多少
Men, materials, you name it.

1021
01:19:04,567 --> 01:19:07,468
上帝，錢是這樣滾入！
And oh, my Lord, how the money rolled in!

1022
01:19:07,670 --> 01:19:10,196
繼續這樣，我不用幹了
At this rate, you'll put me out of business.

1023
01:19:10,406 --> 01:19:14,843
有這些勞工，你可比這鎮上的承包商出更低價
With this pool of slave labor, you can underbid any contractor in town.

1024
01:19:15,411 --> 01:19:18,380
我們提供有用的社區勞務
We're providing a valuable community service.

1025
01:19:18,581 --> 01:19:22,245
對報界來說很動聽，但我要養家活口的
That's fine for the papers, but I've got a family to feed.

1026
01:19:24,922 --> 01:19:26,446
我們走得太遠
We go back a long way.

1027
01:19:27,758 --> 01:19:32,695
我需要這份公路的合同，如果拿不到我就完了
I need this highway contract. I don't get it and I go under. That's a fact.

1028
01:19:33,597 --> 01:19:35,393
嘗嘗我的妻子給你特製的陷餅吧
You have some of this fine pie...

1029
01:19:35,632 --> 01:19:38,964
好好考慮一下
...my missus made for you. You think about that.

1030
01:19:47,244 --> 01:19:49,940
如果我是你對此合同並不擔心
I wouldn't worry too much about this contract.

1031
01:19:50,179 --> 01:19:53,240
我已把人手派至別處
I already got my boys committed elsewhere.

1032
01:19:55,218 --> 01:19:58,277
謝謝你太太的糕餅
You be sure and thank Maisie for this fine pie.

1033
01:19:59,388 --> 01:20:01,548
每筆暗盤交易下
And behind every shady deal...

1034
01:20:01,892 --> 01:20:04,520
賺來的每一分錢
... behind every dollar earned...

1035
01:20:04,794 --> 01:20:07,855
都是由安迪來作記錄的
... there was Andy, keeping the books.

1036
01:20:08,264 --> 01:20:09,526
兩筆存款
Two deposits.

1037
01:20:09,766 --> 01:20:13,896
文尼國際和新格蘭，一天又過去了
Maine National and New England First. Night drops as always, sir.

1038
01:20:44,101 --> 01:20:48,434
-把我的東西拿到洗衣房 -兩套衣服要乾洗的，還有架上的袋子
Get my stuff to the laundry. Two suits for dry-clean and a bag of whatnot.

1039
01:20:48,905 --> 01:20:52,432
如果他們再把我的襯衫漿過了頭，有他們好受的
If they over-starch my shirts again, they'll hear from me.

1040
01:20:52,642 --> 01:20:53,972
我看上去怎麼樣？
How do I look?

1041
01:20:55,012 --> 01:20:57,503
-很不錯 -這是盛大的慈善晚會
- Very nice. - Big charity to-do up Portland way.

1042
01:20:57,713 --> 01:20:59,237
州長也會出席
Governor will be there.

1043
01:21:00,650 --> 01:21:02,116
你要剩下的這些嗎？
You want the rest of this?

1044
01:21:03,453 --> 01:21:05,387
烤的太難吃
Woman can't bake worth shit.

1045
01:21:06,623 --> 01:21:07,954
謝謝，長官
Thank you, sir.

1046
01:21:10,794 --> 01:21:14,025
我聽說這樣的派，他收了不少
He's got his fingers in a lot of pies, from what I hear.

1047
01:21:14,231 --> 01:21:19,066
他有你想像不到的手段，回扣、酬金..
He's got scams you haven't even dreamed of. IKickbacks on his kickbacks.

1048
01:21:19,268 --> 01:21:21,634
黑錢像河一樣流過這
A river of dirty money running through here.

1049
01:21:21,838 --> 01:21:25,672
但他遲早得解釋錢是從何而來的
Sooner or later, he'll have to explain where it came from.

1050
01:21:25,875 --> 01:21:27,638
這就是我牽涉其中的原因
That's where I come in.

1051
01:21:28,245 --> 01:21:30,543
我安排了一切來過濾
I channel it. Filter it. Funnel it.

1052
01:21:30,746 --> 01:21:33,579
股票、債券、市政免稅……
Stocks, securities, tax-free municipals.

1053
01:21:33,916 --> 01:21:37,444
我把錢送到外面，等它們回來的時候……
I send it out into the real world, and when it comes back...

1054
01:21:37,654 --> 01:21:40,623
-純潔得就像個處女 -像洗衣機
- Clean as a virgin's honeypot, huh? - Cleaner.

1055
01:21:41,223 --> 01:21:44,819
到諾頓退休的時候，我已讓他成為百萬富翁了
By the time Norton retires, I'll have made him a millionaire.

1056
01:21:47,164 --> 01:21:51,498
如果被他們抓住的話，他將在自己的監獄穿上這樣的號碼服
If they ever catch on, he'll wind up in here wearing a number himself.

1057
01:21:51,767 --> 01:21:54,463
看來你對我沒有信心
I thought you had more faith in me than that.

1058
01:21:54,670 --> 01:21:57,696
我知道你很能幹，但是總會蛛絲馬跡留下
I know you're good, but all that paper leaves a trail.

1059
01:21:57,907 --> 01:22:01,308
只要有人想細查，FBI，國稅局
Now anybody gets curious, FBI, IRS...

1060
01:22:01,511 --> 01:22:02,499
不管怎樣
...whatever.

1061
01:22:02,946 --> 01:22:04,242
總會有人被牽扯
It'll lead to somebody.

1062
01:22:04,447 --> 01:22:08,316
是的，但不會是我，也不會是典獄長
Sure it is, but not to me, and certainly not to the warden.

1063
01:22:12,688 --> 01:22:13,678
那會是誰？
All right, who?

1064
01:22:13,889 --> 01:22:15,481
蘭度·史蒂文
Randall Stevens.

1065
01:22:16,026 --> 01:22:16,958
誰？
Who?

1066
01:22:17,160 --> 01:22:19,151
從不出聲的拍檔
The "silent" silent partner.

1067
01:22:19,361 --> 01:22:22,422
他是帳戶的持有者，他才有罪
He's the guilty one, the man with the bank accounts.

1068
01:22:22,632 --> 01:22:24,793
他那堿O過濾黑錢過程的起點
It's where the filtering process starts.

1069
01:22:25,000 --> 01:22:27,867
不管他們如何調查，都只會查到他
They trace anything, it'll just lead to him.

1070
01:22:28,472 --> 01:22:29,700
他是什麼人？
But who is he?

1071
01:22:29,905 --> 01:22:33,865
他是一個幻影，幽靈，是兔子哈維的第二個表弟
He's a phantom, an apparition. Second cousin to Harvey the Rabbit.

1072
01:22:34,977 --> 01:22:36,138
我憑空……
I conjured him...

1073
01:22:36,346 --> 01:22:37,710
造出他來
...out of thin air.

1074
01:22:38,514 --> 01:22:41,245
他只存在於文件中罷了
He doesn't exist, except on paper.

1075
01:22:44,321 --> 01:22:46,687
你不能只這麼捏造一個人
You can't just make a person up.

1076
01:22:46,889 --> 01:22:49,983
當然可以，如果你知道我們社會系統的漏洞
Sure you can, if you know how the system works.

1077
01:22:50,494 --> 01:22:53,326
吃驚的是郵政就能幫你做到
It's amazing what you can accomplish by mail.

1078
01:22:53,663 --> 01:22:56,289
史蒂文先生有出生證明書
Mr. Stevens has a birth certificate...

1079
01:22:56,499 --> 01:22:58,626
駕駛執照和社會編號
...driver's license, Social Security.

1080
01:22:58,901 --> 01:22:59,891
你在說笑
You're shitting me.

1081
01:23:00,102 --> 01:23:03,469
他們追查帳戶的話，只是在追查
If they trace any accounts, they'll wind up chasing...

1082
01:23:03,673 --> 01:23:05,401
我幻想出來的人
...a figment of my imagination.

1083
01:23:05,608 --> 01:23:07,599
喔，該死
Well, I'll be damned!

1084
01:23:08,945 --> 01:23:10,673
我沒說過你很能幹嗎？
Did I say you were good?

1085
01:23:11,047 --> 01:23:12,673
該死，你簡直是倫勃朗
Shit, you are Rembrandt.

1086
01:23:13,414 --> 01:23:15,145
有趣的是
The funny thing is...

1087
01:23:15,352 --> 01:23:19,447
……在外面，我是個誠實的人，正直得像桿直箭
...on the outside, I was an honest man, straight as an arrow.

1088
01:23:19,856 --> 01:23:22,187
變成騙子就不得不到監獄堥
I had to come to prison to be a crook.

1089
01:23:31,066 --> 01:23:32,364
你擔心過嗎？
Ever bother you?

1090
01:23:33,803 --> 01:23:36,862
我沒參與，我只是處理收益
I don't run the scams. I just process the profits.

1091
01:23:37,139 --> 01:23:39,130
一條好的分界線，也許吧
A fine line, maybe...

1092
01:23:39,709 --> 01:23:41,767
不過我也建起了圖書館
...but I also built that library...

1093
01:23:41,977 --> 01:23:45,004
來幫助囚犯取得高中文憑
...and used it to help guys get their high school diploma.

1094
01:23:45,214 --> 01:23:47,445
你可知他會何會讓我做所有這些？
Why do you think he lets me do all that?

1095
01:23:47,651 --> 01:23:49,846
讓你開心，好幫他「清洗」……
IKeep you happy and doing the laundry.

1096
01:23:50,053 --> 01:23:51,520
洗的是錢而非床單
Money instead of sheets.

1097
01:23:51,888 --> 01:23:54,481
讓我工作輕鬆，那是交易
Well, I work cheap. That's the tradeoff.

1098
01:24:11,740 --> 01:24:14,369
湯姆·威廉姆斯1965年到肖申克監獄服刑
Tommy Williams came to Shawshank in 1965...

1099
01:24:14,611 --> 01:24:16,840
因非法入室行竊，被判兩年監禁
... on a two-year stretch for B and E.

1100
01:24:17,079 --> 01:24:19,411
那是對私人的非法入侵
That's breaking and entering to you.

1101
01:24:19,682 --> 01:24:23,914
警察在佩妮家後門抓到，他在電視旁鬼鬼祟祟的
Cops caught him sneaking TV sets out the back door of a JC Penney.

1102
01:24:24,353 --> 01:24:25,651
年輕的朋克
Young punk.

1103
01:24:25,855 --> 01:24:27,481
「搖滾」先生
Mr. Rock 'n' Roll...

1104
01:24:27,691 --> 01:24:29,214
過於自大
... cocky as hell.

1105
01:24:29,425 --> 01:24:31,825
快點，老傢伙們，慢得跟糖漿一樣
Come on, old boys. Moving like molasses!

1106
01:24:32,062 --> 01:24:33,825
我乾著急
Making me look bad.

1107
01:24:34,030 --> 01:24:35,826
我們馬上就喜歡上他了
We liked him immediately.

1108
01:24:36,066 --> 01:24:39,797
我從後門出來，像這樣捧著電視機
I'm backing out the door and I got the TV like this.

1109
01:24:40,486 --> 01:24:43,886
一件大的老傢伙，我都看不到了，然後我聽到這個聲音
A big old thing. I couldn't see shit. Then I hear this voice.

1110
01:24:44,524 --> 01:24:46,492
別動，舉起手來！
"Freeze, kid, hands in the air."

1111
01:24:47,343 --> 01:24:51,803
我站在那堙A捧著電視機，他又說：
I was standing there, holding onto that TV. Finally the voice says:

1112
01:24:52,013 --> 01:24:55,813
「你聽到我說的嗎？」，我說，「是的，先生」
"You hear what I said, boy?" I say, " Yes, sir. I did.

1113
01:24:56,018 --> 01:24:59,475
但我掉落東西，你會告我毀壞他人財物
But if I drop this, you get me on destruction of property too."

1114
01:25:03,959 --> 01:25:06,256
你曾在卡士文服刑，是嗎？
You done some stretch in Cashman, right?

1115
01:25:06,762 --> 01:25:10,720
是的，那兒要好過得多
Yeah, that was an easy piece of time, let me tell you.

1116
01:25:11,000 --> 01:25:12,933
週末有休假，工作也很有計劃
Weekend furloughs. Work programs.

1117
01:25:13,134 --> 01:25:14,192
不像這
Not like here.

1118
01:25:14,402 --> 01:25:16,836
看來你在新英格蘭都呆在車
Sounds like you done time all over.

1119
01:25:17,272 --> 01:25:19,673
我十三歲出道，哪堻ㄔh過
I've been in and out since I was 13.

1120
01:25:19,875 --> 01:25:21,826
說說看，也許我也去過那
Name it, chances are I've been there.

1121
01:25:21,827 --> 01:25:24,489
也許你應轉行了
Perhaps you should try a new profession.

1122
01:25:25,931 --> 01:25:27,489
我是說
What I mean is...

1123
01:25:27,833 --> 01:25:31,269
……你不是個一流的小偷，你該試試別的
...you're not a very good thief. You should try something else.

1124
01:25:31,504 --> 01:25:34,734
是嗎？你以為你懂這個？
Yeah, what the hell you know about it, Capone?

1125
01:25:35,039 --> 01:25:36,633
你怎會進來的？
What are you in for?

1126
01:25:36,910 --> 01:25:37,898
我嗎？
Me?

1127
01:25:40,346 --> 01:25:42,007
律師坑了我
A lawyer fucked me.

1128
01:25:45,919 --> 01:25:48,888
這兒所有人都是無辜的，你不知道嗎？
Everybody's innocent in here. Don't you know that?

1129
01:25:56,795 --> 01:26:01,199
後來知道，湯姆竟然有妻子和剛出生的女兒
As it turned out, Tommy had himself a young wife and a new baby girl.

1130
01:26:01,667 --> 01:26:03,795
也許他想到她們在街上流蕩
Maybe he thought of them on the streets...

1131
01:26:04,002 --> 01:26:06,493
孩子長大卻不知道父親是誰
... or his child growing up not knowing her daddy.

1132
01:26:06,805 --> 01:26:08,171
不管為什麼，總之
Whatever it was...

1133
01:26:08,506 --> 01:26:10,941
他竟努力起來了
... something lit a fire under that boy's ass.

1134
01:26:14,780 --> 01:26:17,648
我想考取高校文憑
Thought I might try for my high school equivalency.

1135
01:26:17,850 --> 01:26:20,376
聽說你已經幫了很多人了
Hear you helped a couple of fellas with that.

1136
01:26:21,721 --> 01:26:23,950
我不會在失敗者身上浪費時間的
I don't waste time with losers, Tommy.

1137
01:26:25,358 --> 01:26:27,849
我再也不是失敗者了
I ain't no goddamn loser.

1138
01:26:29,596 --> 01:26:31,426
-你當真？ -是
- You mean that? - Yeah.

1139
01:26:33,099 --> 01:26:34,532
你真的是認真的？
You really mean that?

1140
01:26:35,568 --> 01:26:36,932
是的，先生，絕對是真的
Yes, sir, I do.

1141
01:26:37,136 --> 01:26:39,104
好，因為我們要做就要……
Good. Because if we do this...

1142
01:26:39,305 --> 01:26:43,264
……有始有終，絕對不能半途而廢
...we do it all the way, a hundred percent, nothing half-assed.

1143
01:26:43,510 --> 01:26:45,306
問題是……
Thing is, see...

1144
01:26:46,578 --> 01:26:48,103
我識字不多
...I don't read so good.

1145
01:26:49,282 --> 01:26:50,373
好吧
"Well."

1146
01:26:52,385 --> 01:26:54,113
你不識字
You don't read...

1147
01:26:54,354 --> 01:26:55,877
就這樣
...so well.

1148
01:26:58,224 --> 01:26:59,713
我們就由它開始
We'll get to that.

1149
01:27:04,163 --> 01:27:06,289
就這樣，安迪開始給湯姆上課
So Andy took Tommy under his wing.

1150
01:27:06,498 --> 01:27:09,127
從最基礎的字母開始教
Started walking him through his ABC's.

1151
01:27:11,270 --> 01:27:13,466
湯姆學得很快
Tommy took to it pretty well too.

1152
01:27:13,739 --> 01:27:16,503
從不知道自己的聰明
Boy found brains he never knew he had.

1153
01:27:18,845 --> 01:27:22,280
沒過多久，安迪開始教他課程內容
Before long, Andy started him on his course requirements.

1154
01:27:22,481 --> 01:27:24,142
他很喜歡這個孩子
He really liked the kid.

1155
01:27:24,350 --> 01:27:27,911
幫一個孩子上進讓他很快樂
Gave him a thrill to help a youngster crawl off the shit heap.

1156
01:27:28,421 --> 01:27:30,685
但那不是唯一的原因
But that wasn't the only reason.

1157
01:27:31,390 --> 01:27:33,586
監獄堛漱擗l很緩慢
Prison time is slow time.

1158
01:27:34,060 --> 01:27:36,654
要用某些事情來消磨時間
So you do what you can to keep going.

1159
01:27:36,996 --> 01:27:39,055
有人收集郵票
Some fellas collect stamps.

1160
01:27:39,465 --> 01:27:41,932
有人收集火柴盒
Others build matchstick houses.

1161
01:27:42,534 --> 01:27:45,197
安迪建起了圖書館
Andy built a library.

1162
01:27:45,704 --> 01:27:47,639
現在他需要新的計劃
Now he needed a new project.

1163
01:27:48,506 --> 01:27:49,997
那就是湯姆
Tommy was it.

1164
01:27:50,642 --> 01:27:54,636
那和他多年來雕磨石頭的原因一樣
It was the same reason he spent years shaping and polishing those rocks.

1165
01:27:55,180 --> 01:27:58,412
也如同他把美女的畫像掛在牆上的原因
The same reason he hung his fantasy girlies on the wall.

1166
01:27:59,319 --> 01:28:00,581
在監獄
In prison...

1167
01:28:00,853 --> 01:28:04,583
一個人不能讓心堛霾
... a man will do most anything to keep his mind occupied.

1168
01:28:05,358 --> 01:28:10,226
在1966年，湯姆剛要參加考試的時候
By 1966, right about the time Tommy was getting ready to take his exams...

1169
01:28:10,462 --> 01:28:12,658
可愛的瑞奎爾（Raquel）出現了
... it was lovely Raquel.

1170
01:28:29,215 --> 01:28:30,203
時間到
Time.

1171
01:28:36,255 --> 01:28:37,243
好了嗎？
Well?

1172
01:28:38,858 --> 01:28:40,984
真的是一團糟
Well, it's for shit.

1173
01:28:41,493 --> 01:28:44,327
我白花了一年時間在這狗屎上面
I wasted a whole year of my time with this bullshit.

1174
01:28:44,529 --> 01:28:46,020
也許沒有你想的那麼糟
It's probably not that bad.

1175
01:28:46,231 --> 01:28:50,463
比我想像中的還要糟，就像在考中文
I didn't get a thing right. It might as well have been in Chinese.

1176
01:28:50,670 --> 01:28:52,399
看看你得了多少分？
Let's see how the score comes out.

1177
01:28:52,604 --> 01:28:55,573
我來告訴你吧
I'll tell you how the goddamn score comes out.

1178
01:28:57,510 --> 01:28:58,874
兩分
Two points, right there!

1179
01:28:59,078 --> 01:29:00,636
那就是你該死的考試
There's your goddamn score!

1180
01:29:00,880 --> 01:29:04,577
什麼貓爬上樹，5乘以5是25
Goddamn cats crawling up trees, 5 times 5 is 25...

1181
01:29:05,517 --> 01:29:07,145
去死吧
Fuck this place!

1182
01:29:07,386 --> 01:29:08,512
他媽的
Fuck it!

1183
01:29:27,673 --> 01:29:28,935
我感覺很差
I feel bad.

1184
01:29:29,141 --> 01:29:30,336
我令他失望了
I let him down.

1185
01:29:30,542 --> 01:29:32,271
不是這樣，孩子
That's crap, kid.

1186
01:29:32,478 --> 01:29:33,809
他以你為榮
He's proud of you.

1187
01:29:34,146 --> 01:29:37,014
我跟他是老朋友，我很清楚他的性格
We're old friends, I know him as good as anybody.

1188
01:29:37,216 --> 01:29:38,774
聰明的夥伴，不是嗎？
Smart fellow, ain't he?

1189
01:29:38,984 --> 01:29:42,113
就像剛進來時一樣聰明，他以前是個銀行家
Smart as they come. He was a banker on the outside.

1190
01:29:42,320 --> 01:29:44,551
他為什麼被抓進來？
What's he in here for anyway?

1191
01:29:44,890 --> 01:29:45,858
謀殺
Murder.

1192
01:29:47,325 --> 01:29:48,689
你說什麼？
The hell, you say.

1193
01:29:50,829 --> 01:29:53,162
人不可以貌相
You wouldn't think it to look at the guy.

1194
01:29:54,399 --> 01:29:58,496
在床上捉到妻子和一個高爾夫選手，把他們兩個一起解決了
Caught his wife in bed with some golf pro. Greased them both.

1195
01:30:06,180 --> 01:30:07,112
怎麼了?
What?

1196
01:30:08,649 --> 01:30:10,708
大約四年前
About four years ago...

1197
01:30:11,485 --> 01:30:15,182
我在湯瑪斯獄服刑
...I was in Thomaston on a two-to-three stretch.

1198
01:30:15,729 --> 01:30:17,025
我偷了一輛車
I stole a car.

1199
01:30:17,398 --> 01:30:19,389
這是很不應該的事
It was a dumb-fuck thing to do.

1200
01:30:19,866 --> 01:30:22,096
在出獄前六個月
About six months left to go...

1201
01:30:22,403 --> 01:30:24,302
我有了個新同房
...I get a new cellmate in.

1202
01:30:25,004 --> 01:30:26,632
艾馬·布萊奇
Elmo Blatch.

1203
01:30:27,341 --> 01:30:28,672
一個強壯、暴躁的混蛋
Big, twitchy fucker.

1204
01:30:29,543 --> 01:30:33,034
人見人憎的那種，明白我的意思嗎？
IKind of roomie you pray you don't get. You know what I'm saying?

1205
01:30:33,247 --> 01:30:35,976
刑期是六到十二年，持械搶劫
Six-to-twelve, armed burglary.

1206
01:30:36,249 --> 01:30:38,513
他說自己犯了不少案子
Said he pulled hundreds of jobs.

