01:43:39,190 --> 01:43:41,681
一個沒有記憶的溫暖地方
A warm place with no memory.

1384
01:43:44,929 --> 01:43:46,863
開間小旅館
Open up a little hotel...

1385
01:43:48,567 --> 01:43:50,056
就在沙灘邊上
...right on the beach.

1386
01:43:50,669 --> 01:43:52,863
買艘不值錢的舊船回來
Buy some worthless old boat...

1387
01:43:53,404 --> 01:43:55,032
把它翻新
...and fix it up new.

1388
01:43:57,775 --> 01:43:59,004
載著我的客人
Take my guests out...

1389
01:43:59,845 --> 01:44:01,210
出海釣魚
...charter fishing.

1390
01:44:05,050 --> 01:44:06,778
聖哈塔尼奧
Zihuatanejo.

1391
01:44:10,322 --> 01:44:14,189
在那種地方，我需要個能找到東西的人
In a place like that, I could use a man that knows how to get things.

1392
01:44:20,733 --> 01:44:23,565
我覺得外面的社會可能不適合我
I don't think I could make it on the outside.

1393
01:44:30,242 --> 01:44:32,300
我的大半生都在這奡蝜L
I been in here most of my life.

1394
01:44:33,746 --> 01:44:35,509
我已經是這堛漱@部分了
I'm an institutional man now.

1395
01:44:36,415 --> 01:44:38,144
就像布魯克那樣
Just like Brooks was.

1396
01:44:39,617 --> 01:44:41,313
你看輕了你自己
You underestimate yourself.

1397
01:44:41,886 --> 01:44:43,479
我不這樣看
I don't think so.

1398
01:44:47,326 --> 01:44:51,261
在此我能供應物品給你，但是……
In here I'm the guy who can get things for you, sure, but...

1399
01:44:52,031 --> 01:44:54,555
在外面你只需要電話簿黃頁分類
...outside all you need is the Yellow Pages.

1400
01:44:54,766 --> 01:44:56,996
我不知道如何開始
Hell, I wouldn't know where to begin.

1401
01:44:59,138 --> 01:45:00,764
太平洋？
Pacific Ocean?

1402
01:45:01,172 --> 01:45:02,400
Shit.

1403
01:45:02,773 --> 01:45:04,970
那麼大的地方會嚇死我的
Scare me to death, something that big.

1404
01:45:05,176 --> 01:45:06,474
我不怕
Not me.

1405
01:45:07,679 --> 01:45:10,443
我沒開槍殺我妻子，我也沒開槍殺她的情人
I didn't shoot my wife, and I didn't shoot her lover.

1406
01:45:12,184 --> 01:45:15,415
不論我犯了什麼錯，我都已補償了
Whatever mistakes I made, I've paid for them and then some.

1407
01:45:16,455 --> 01:45:17,944
一間旅館和一條船
That hotel, that boat...

1408
01:45:19,724 --> 01:45:21,955
我要的並不太多
I don't think that's too much to ask.

1409
01:45:26,864 --> 01:45:29,299
我勸你不要再想了
You shouldn't be doing this to yourself.

1410
01:45:29,501 --> 01:45:31,525
那只是你的夢想罷了
This is just shitty pipe dreams.

1411
01:45:31,970 --> 01:45:34,438
墨西哥在遙遠的天邊，而你在這
Mexico is way down there and you're in here...

1412
01:45:34,639 --> 01:45:36,197
這才是現實
...and that's the way it is.

1413
01:45:36,541 --> 01:45:39,375
是的，是這樣
Yeah, right. That's the way it is.

1414
01:45:40,879 --> 01:45:43,278
它在遠方，而我在這
It's down there and I'm in here.

1415
01:45:45,850 --> 01:45:48,581
我想只有一個簡單的選擇
I guess it comes down to a simple choice.

1416
01:45:51,489 --> 01:45:52,979
要麼忙著活……
Get busy living...

1417
01:45:54,359 --> 01:45:56,385
要麼忙著死
...or get busy dying.

1418
01:46:00,166 --> 01:46:00,962
安迪

1419
01:46:05,004 --> 01:46:05,868
瑞德

1420
01:46:08,506 --> 01:46:11,237
如果你能出去的話，幫我做件事
If you ever get out of here, do me a favor.

1421
01:46:11,443 --> 01:46:13,706
當然可以，安迪，什麼事都行
Sure, Andy. Anything.

1422
01:46:15,581 --> 01:46:19,448
布克斯頓附近有個草場，你知道在哪媔隉H
There's a big hayfield up near Buxton. You know where Buxton is?

1423
01:46:20,919 --> 01:46:24,046
-那埵陶\多牧場 -有一個很特別……
- A lot of hayfields up there. - One in particular.

1424
01:46:24,255 --> 01:46:28,192
它有很長的石牆，北邊的盡頭有棵橡樹
It's got a long rock wall with a big oak tree at the north end.

1425
01:46:28,394 --> 01:46:31,260
像佛洛斯特的詩描繪的那樣 「佛洛斯特（Robert Frost）：美國著名詩人」
It's like something out of a Robert Frost poem.

1426
01:46:32,197 --> 01:46:34,688
那是我向我太太求婚的地方
It's where I asked my wife to marry me.

1427
01:46:36,100 --> 01:46:38,193
我們到那堨h野餐
We went there for a picnic...

1428
01:46:38,604 --> 01:46:40,697
還在橡樹下做愛
...and made love under that oak...

1429
01:46:41,372 --> 01:46:43,603
我向她求婚，她答應了
...and I asked and she said yes.

1430
01:46:47,613 --> 01:46:49,443
答應我，瑞德
Promise me, Red.

1431
01:46:50,282 --> 01:46:51,908
如果你出去的話
If you ever get out...

1432
01:46:52,117 --> 01:46:53,607
找到那
...find that spot.

1433
01:46:54,787 --> 01:46:59,621
在牆角下，有塊與眾不同的石頭……
At the base of that wall, there's a rock that has no earthly business in Maine.

1434
01:47:00,759 --> 01:47:03,784
一塊黑色的火山玻璃石
Piece of black, volcanic glass.

1435
01:47:06,465 --> 01:47:09,126
下面埋著我想給你的東西
Something's buried under it I want you to have.

1436
01:47:09,902 --> 01:47:11,130
是什麼，安迪？
What, Andy?

1437
01:47:11,569 --> 01:47:13,299
埋在那堛漪O什麼？
What's buried under there?

1438
01:47:14,907 --> 01:47:16,772
你自己挖出來……
You'll have to pry it up...

1439
01:47:16,974 --> 01:47:18,237
……就知道了
...to see.

1440
01:47:24,116 --> 01:47:26,083
不，我告訴你，他……
No, I'm telling you. The guy is...

1441
01:47:26,751 --> 01:47:28,480
他只是在開玩笑
He's talking funny.

1442
01:47:29,587 --> 01:47:31,282
我真的很擔心他
I'm really worried about him.

1443
01:47:31,689 --> 01:47:33,122
那就好好看著他吧
Let's keep an eye on him.

1444
01:47:33,324 --> 01:47:36,590
白天還可以，但晚上怎麼辦？
That's fine during the day, but at night he's all alone.

1445
01:47:38,029 --> 01:47:39,156
上帝
Oh, Lord.

1446
01:47:40,498 --> 01:47:41,328
什麼事？
What?

1447
01:47:42,835 --> 01:47:45,599
安迪今天到我這堥蚢L
Andy come down to the loading dock today.

1448
01:47:45,804 --> 01:47:47,897
他問我要了捆繩索
He asked me for a length of rope.

1449
01:47:48,105 --> 01:47:48,935
繩索？
Rope?

1450
01:47:49,139 --> 01:47:50,801
六英尺長
Six feet long.

1451
01:47:51,042 --> 01:47:52,407
那你給他了？
And you gave it to him.

1452
01:47:53,278 --> 01:47:55,074
當然為什麼不呢？
Sure. Why wouldn't I?

1453
01:47:55,279 --> 01:47:56,837
上帝！海伍德
Jesus! Heywood.

1454
01:47:57,448 --> 01:47:59,416
我怎麼知道？
How was I supposed to know?

1455
01:47:59,617 --> 01:48:01,175
還記得布魯克斯嗎？
Remember Brooks Hatlen?

1456
01:48:03,188 --> 01:48:05,121
不，安迪不會那樣做的
Andy would never do that.

1457
01:48:05,724 --> 01:48:06,782
永遠不會
Never.

1458
01:48:08,861 --> 01:48:10,192
我不敢肯定
I don't know.

1459
01:48:13,031 --> 01:48:15,055
人總有脆弱的一刻
Every man has his breaking point.

1460
01:48:17,402 --> 01:48:19,666
快點要收工了
Lickety-split. Want to get home.

1461
01:48:19,971 --> 01:48:21,734
還差一點點了
Just about finished, sir.

1462
01:48:38,857 --> 01:48:40,483
今晚有三筆存款
Three deposits tonight.

1463
01:48:48,466 --> 01:48:50,367
把我的衣服拿到洗衣處去
Get my stuff down to the laundry.

1464
01:48:50,568 --> 01:48:52,196
還要擦一下我的鞋子
And shine my shoes.

1465
01:48:52,403 --> 01:48:55,339
我要它們看起來像鏡子一樣亮，好的，先生
- I want them looking like mirrors. - Yes, sir.

1466
01:49:00,845 --> 01:49:02,313
你能回來真好，安迪
It's good having you back.

1467
01:49:03,247 --> 01:49:05,113
你不在的話，一切都不一樣了
Place wasn't the same without you.

1468
01:49:51,996 --> 01:49:53,054
熄燈
Lights out!

1469
01:50:25,897 --> 01:50:28,421
那是個輾轉難眠的長夜
I've had some long nights in stir.

1470
01:50:28,966 --> 01:50:31,629
孤獨的黑暗中只有思想
Alone in the dark with nothing but your thoughts...

1471
01:50:31,836 --> 01:50:34,498
時間像把快刀
... time can draw out like a blade.

1472
01:50:39,845 --> 01:50:42,836
那是我一生中最漫長的夜晚
That was the longest night of my life.

1473
01:50:58,697 --> 01:50:59,857
清點人數
Give me a count!

1474
01:51:04,368 --> 01:51:07,202
南邊三樓，人齊了
Tier 3 south, clear!

1475
01:51:10,341 --> 01:51:13,505
二樓245囚室的人不見了
Man missing on tier 2, cell 245!

1476
01:51:13,711 --> 01:51:14,769
德弗瑞恩！
Dufresne!

1477
01:51:15,313 --> 01:51:17,746
快出來！不要耍花樣
Come out. You're holding up the show!

1478
01:51:20,885 --> 01:51:24,287
別要我下來打爆你的頭
Don't make me come down or I'll thump your skull for you!

1479
01:51:31,863 --> 01:51:35,697
他媽的，你不要耽誤我，我還有很多事要做
Damn it, you're putting me behind! I got a schedule to keep.

1480
01:51:35,900 --> 01:51:39,199
你最好是病了或者死了
You'd better be sick or dead in there. I shit you not!

1481
01:51:39,403 --> 01:51:40,734
你聽到了嗎？
You hear me?

1482
01:51:46,845 --> 01:51:48,938
啊，我的上帝！
Oh, my Holy God.

1483
01:52:05,930 --> 01:52:08,491
查問這堛漕C一個犯人
I want every man on this cellblock questioned.

1484
01:52:08,934 --> 01:52:11,493
-從他的好朋友開始 -誰？
- Start with that friend of his. - Who?

1485
01:52:11,934 --> 01:52:13,493
他！

1486
01:52:14,072 --> 01:52:15,630
打開237號的門
Open 237.

1487
01:52:19,144 --> 01:52:22,806
你什麼意思，「他不在這了」？別跟我說這種話
What do you mean, "He just wasn't here"? Don't say that to me.

1488
01:52:23,681 --> 01:52:25,013
別再這樣說
Don't tell me that again.

1489
01:52:25,216 --> 01:52:26,241
但是長官，他真的不在那
But sir, he wasn't.

1490
01:52:26,484 --> 01:52:29,943
我看得見！你認為我瞎了嗎？
I can see that, Haig! Think I'm blind?

1491
01:52:30,621 --> 01:52:32,020
這就是你想說的嗎？
Is that what you're saying?

1492
01:52:32,224 --> 01:52:34,885
-我瞎了嗎？ -沒有！長官
- Am I blind, Haig? - No, sir!

1493
01:52:35,794 --> 01:52:38,284
那你呢？你瞎了嗎？
What about you. You blind?

1494
01:52:38,796 --> 01:52:41,357
-告訴我這是什麼？ -昨晚的查房記錄
- Tell me what this is. - Last night's count.

1495
01:52:41,565 --> 01:52:44,864
你看到德弗瑞恩的名字嗎？我確定，就在那
You see Dufresne's name there? I sure do. Right there.

1496
01:52:45,069 --> 01:52:46,400
「德弗瑞恩」
"Dufresne."

1497
01:52:48,072 --> 01:52:49,540
他熄燈的時候
He was in his cell...

1498
01:52:49,773 --> 01:52:50,742
還在囚室堛
...at lights out.

1499
01:52:50,942 --> 01:52:53,206
因此今早他也應該在
Reasonable he'd be here in the morning.

1500
01:52:54,246 --> 01:52:55,872
我要找到他
I want him found.

1501
01:52:56,081 --> 01:52:59,538
不是明天，不是早飯後，是現在
Not tomorrow, not after breakfast. Now!

1502
01:52:59,784 --> 01:53:00,979
是的，長官
Yes, sir.

1503
01:53:01,987 --> 01:53:04,251
快走
Let's go. Move your butts.

1504
01:53:07,658 --> 01:53:08,648
站好
Stand.

1505
01:53:10,095 --> 01:53:11,153
那麼？
Well?

1506
01:53:14,599 --> 01:53:15,587
那麼，什麼？
Well, what?

1507
01:53:15,800 --> 01:53:19,259
你們常在一起，親密得像做賊一樣
I see you two all the time. You're thick as thieves, you are.

1508
01:53:20,337 --> 01:53:21,827
他肯定對你說過些什麼
He must have said something.

1509
01:53:22,573 --> 01:53:24,098
沒有，先生，獄長
No, sir, Warden.

1510
01:53:24,475 --> 01:53:25,443
什麼都沒說
Not a word.

1511
01:53:27,278 --> 01:53:29,839
主啊，這是個奇跡
Lord, it's a miracle!

1512
01:53:30,447 --> 01:53:33,007
人就像屁一樣在風中消失了
Man vanished like a fart in the wind.

1513
01:53:33,684 --> 01:53:34,845
什麼都沒留下
Nothing left...

1514
01:53:35,687 --> 01:53:38,416
只剩下窗台上的石頭
...but some damn rocks on a windowsill.

1515
01:53:38,622 --> 01:53:41,353
和那牆上的小妞，問問她吧
And that cupcake on the wall. Let's ask her.

1516
01:53:41,559 --> 01:53:43,322
也許她知道些什麼
Maybe she knows.

1517
01:53:43,562 --> 01:53:46,291
你想說什麼？
What say there, fuzzy-britches? Feel like talking?

1518
01:53:47,732 --> 01:53:49,028
我想沒有
Guess not.

1519
01:53:49,600 --> 01:53:51,796
為什麼她有點特別？
Why should she be any different?

1520
01:53:52,871 --> 01:53:54,532
這是一個陰謀
This is a conspiracy.

1521
01:53:55,172 --> 01:53:57,004
肯定是的
That's what this is.

1522
01:53:57,608 --> 01:54:01,340
一個該死的大陰謀
One big, damn conspiracy!

1523
01:54:01,613 --> 01:54:03,604
所有人都有參與
And everyone's in on it!

1524
01:54:04,248 --> 01:54:05,408
包括她
Including her!

1525
01:54:40,452 --> 01:54:42,147
在1966年
In 1966...

1526
01:54:42,354 --> 01:54:44,754
安迪·德弗瑞恩從肖申克監獄……
... Andy Dufresne escaped...

1527
01:54:44,956 --> 01:54:46,514
逃了出去
... from Shawshank Prison.

1528
01:54:48,760 --> 01:54:51,319
他們只能找到泥塘中的囚衣……
All they found was a muddy set of prison clothes...

1529
01:54:51,962 --> 01:54:53,487
一塊肥皂……
... a bar of soap...

1530
01:54:53,697 --> 01:54:55,255
和一個很舊的手槌
... and an old rock hammer...

1531
01:54:55,466 --> 01:54:57,934
幾乎快被削成一小塊
... damn near worn down to the nub.

1532
01:55:02,439 --> 01:55:07,206
我曾認為用手槌要六百年才能掘通的隧道
I had thought it'd take a man 600 years to tunnel through the wall with it.

1533
01:55:07,845 --> 01:55:10,474
安迪用不到二十年就辦到了
Old Andy did it in less than 20.

1534
01:55:28,766 --> 01:55:31,064
安迪很喜歡地質學
Oh, Andy loved geology.

1535
01:55:31,836 --> 01:55:34,998
我能想像這歸功於他一絲不茍的本性
I imagine it appealed to his meticulous nature.

1536
01:55:35,407 --> 01:55:37,238
如果這埵酗@段冰河時期
An ice age here...

1537
01:55:37,675 --> 01:55:40,166
百萬年後，山脈就會在那塈峖
... million years of mountain building there.

1538
01:55:41,179 --> 01:55:44,011
地質學是關於壓力和時間的研究
Geology is the study of pressure and time.

1539
01:55:44,849 --> 01:55:46,840
需要的僅僅就是這些
That's all it takes, really.

1540
01:55:47,585 --> 01:55:48,676
壓力……
Pressure...

1541
01:55:49,321 --> 01:55:50,581
……和時間
... and time.

1542
01:55:51,922 --> 01:55:53,982
還有一張大海報
That and a big goddamn poster.

1543
01:55:58,028 --> 01:55:58,961
就像我說的那樣
Like I said...

1544
01:55:59,464 --> 01:56:03,456
監獄堛漱H都會找事情來消磨時間
... in prison, a man will do anything to keep his mind occupied.

1545
01:56:06,270 --> 01:56:11,072
看起來安迪的愛好是把他的牆搬運到廣場上
Seems Andy's favorite hobby was toting his wall out into the exercise yard...

1546
01:56:11,608 --> 01:56:13,542
每次一把
... a handful at a time.

1547
01:56:14,845 --> 01:56:16,904
我猜在湯姆被殺後
I guess after Tommy was killed...

1548
01:56:17,114 --> 01:56:20,083
安迪覺得他在此呆得已夠久了
... Andy decided he'd been here long enough.

1549
01:56:20,284 --> 01:56:22,845
盡快，我要回家了
Lickety-split. I want to get home.

1550
01:56:23,587 --> 01:56:25,613
我馬上就好了
I'm just about finished, sir.

1551
01:56:47,077 --> 01:56:49,011
今晚有三筆存款
Three deposits tonight.

1552
01:56:56,321 --> 01:56:58,618
安迪照他的吩咐
Andy did like he was told.

1553
01:56:58,822 --> 01:57:02,314
把鞋擦得閃閃發亮
Buffed those shoes to a high mirror-shine.

1554
01:57:05,996 --> 01:57:08,295
警衛完全沒有注意到
The guards simply didn't notice.

1555
01:57:08,599 --> 01:57:10,067
我也沒有
Neither did I.

1556
01:57:10,268 --> 01:57:11,791
說真的
I mean, seriously...

1557
01:57:12,002 --> 01:57:14,995
誰會留意別人穿的鞋子呢？
... how often do you really look at a man's shoes?

1558
01:59:18,563 --> 01:59:21,725
安迪朝向自由爬了五百碼
Andy crawled to freedom through 500 yards...

1559
01:59:21,965 --> 01:59:25,299
我難以想像有多臭的下水道
... of shit-smelling foulness I can't even imagine.

1560
01:59:26,304 --> 01:59:28,635
或許我只是不想去爬
Or maybe I just don't want to.

1561
01:59:33,044 --> 01:59:35,409
五百碼
Five hundred yards.

1562
01:59:35,913 --> 01:59:38,974
有五個足球場那麼長
That's the length of five football fields.

1563
01:59:39,617 --> 01:59:42,176
有半英里左右
Just shy of half a mile.

1564
02:00:37,407 --> 02:00:42,004
第二天早上，就在那海報被撕下來的時候
The next morning, right about the time Raquel was spilling her secret...

1565
02:00:42,313 --> 02:00:45,145
一個從未出現過的人
... a man nobody ever laid eyes on before...

1566
02:00:45,382 --> 02:00:47,976
走進了緬因州國家銀行
... strolled into the Maine National Bank.

1567
02:00:48,553 --> 02:00:51,715
在那一刻前，他從來是不存在的
Until that moment, he didn't exist.

1568
02:00:52,290 --> 02:00:54,656
-除了在紙上 -我可以幫忙嗎？
- Except on paper. - May I help you?

1569
02:00:55,059 --> 02:00:56,992
他有所有正確的身份證明文件……
He had all the proper ID...

1570
02:00:57,194 --> 02:01:00,891
駕駛執照、出生證明、社會安全證……
... driver's license, birth certificate, Social Security card...

1571
02:01:01,331 --> 02:01:03,857
簽名也是正確的
And the signature was a spot-on match.

1572
02:01:04,068 --> 02:01:07,162
不能再為你服務真的很遺憾
I must say I'm sorry to be losing your business.

1573
02:01:07,371 --> 02:01:09,100
希望你在國外生活愉快
I hope you'll enjoy living abroad.

1574
02:01:09,907 --> 02:01:10,998
謝謝
Thank you.

1575
02:01:11,675 --> 02:01:12,836
我想我會的
I'm sure I will.

1576
02:01:13,745 --> 02:01:17,077
先生，這是你的本票，還有別的嗎？
Here's your cashier's check, sir. Will there be anything else?

1577
02:01:17,282 --> 02:01:18,270
請問
Please.

1578
02:01:18,849 --> 02:01:21,340
你能幫我把它寄出嗎？
Would you add this to your outgoing mail?

1579
02:01:21,853 --> 02:01:23,046
我很樂意
I'd be happy to.

1580
02:01:24,855 --> 02:01:26,187
-再見 -走好，先生
Good day, sir.

1581
02:01:27,125 --> 02:01:31,562
史蒂文先生那天早上去了將近十二家銀行
Mr. Stevens visited nearly a dozen banks in the Portland area that morning.

1582
02:01:32,029 --> 02:01:33,621
加起來
All told, he blew town...

1583
02:01:33,831 --> 02:01:38,666
他總共提取了三十七萬諾頓獄長的錢
... with better than $370,000 of Warden Norton's money.

1584
02:01:39,370 --> 02:01:42,134
作為十九年的賠償
Severance pay for 19 years.

1585
02:01:49,380 --> 02:01:51,574
早上好，波特蘭時報
Good morning, Portland Daily Bugle.

1586
02:01:52,051 --> 02:01:54,781
「肖申克監獄,貪污謀殺」

1587
02:02:02,695 --> 02:02:05,061
「主的審判迅速降臨」

1588
02:02:21,680 --> 02:02:24,513
「親愛的典獄長,你說的對」

1589
02:02:24,550 --> 02:02:26,347
「得救之道,就在其中」

1590
02:02:43,734 --> 02:02:46,670
拜倫·哈德利？你有權保持沉默
Byron Hadley? You have the right to remain silent.

1591
02:02:46,938 --> 02:02:51,274
否則你所說的一切都將對你不利
If you give up this right, anything you say can be held against you in court.

1592
02:02:52,510 --> 02:02:55,970
我雖沒有親眼看到，但我聽說他被帶走時
I wasn't there to see, but I hear Byron Hadley sobbed like a girl...

1593
02:02:56,180 --> 02:02:57,671
哭得像個娘們
... when they took him away.

1594
02:03:03,954 --> 02:03:06,956
諾頓沒有靜靜離開的意思
Norton had no intention of going that quietly.

1595
02:03:23,808 --> 02:03:24,638
森姆·諾頓？
Samuel Norton.

1596
02:03:25,443 --> 02:03:27,876
我們有拘捕令，開門！
We have a warrant for your arrest. Open up.

1597
02:03:32,617 --> 02:03:33,708
開門吧
Open the door.

1598
02:03:34,251 --> 02:03:35,514
我不知是哪把鑰匙
I'm not sure which key.

1599
02:03:45,662 --> 02:03:47,596
別緊張，諾頓
Make it easy on yourself, Norton!

1600
02:03:59,109 --> 02:04:02,568
我想知道當子彈穿過他的頭的時候
I like to think the last thing that went through his head...

1601
02:04:02,779 --> 02:04:04,371
他在想些什麼
... other than that bullet...

1602
02:04:04,581 --> 02:04:09,019
是在想該死的安迪.德弗瑞恩到底是如何擊敗他？
... was to wonder how the hell Andy Dufresne ever got the best of him.

1603
02:04:11,522 --> 02:04:14,979
諾頓獄長一夥倒台之後
Not long after the warden deprived us of his company...

1604
02:04:15,259 --> 02:04:17,318
我收到了張明信片
... I got a postcard in the mail.

1605
02:04:18,796 --> 02:04:21,629
它是空白的，但是郵戳是……
It was blank, but the postmark said...

1606
02:04:21,831 --> 02:04:23,960
漢格堡，德薩斯州的
... Fort Hancock, Texas.

1607
02:04:24,201 --> 02:04:25,567
漢格堡
Fort Hancock...

1608
02:04:25,836 --> 02:04:27,566
就在邊境那
... right on the border.

1609
02:04:27,972 --> 02:04:29,963
安迪就是從那堨X國的
That's where Andy crossed.

1610
02:04:30,541 --> 02:04:34,671
當我想到他開車向南走的時候
When I picture him heading south in his own car with the top down...

1611
02:04:35,013 --> 02:04:37,242
我總會笑起來
... it always makes me laugh.

1612
02:04:39,082 --> 02:04:40,640
安迪·德弗瑞恩
Andy Dufresne...

1613
02:04:41,018 --> 02:04:43,044
爬過了那臭屎溝
... who crawled through a river of shit...

1614
02:04:43,254 --> 02:04:45,653
然後乾乾淨淨的到另一邊去了
... and came out clean on the other side.

1615
02:04:46,491 --> 02:04:47,856
安迪·德弗瑞恩
Andy Dufresne...

1616
02:04:48,660 --> 02:04:50,251
向太平洋進發
... headed for the Pacific.

1617
02:04:53,231 --> 02:04:55,392
哈德利抓住他的頭，對嗎？
Hadley's got him by the throat, right?

1618
02:04:55,598 --> 02:04:59,399
他說，「我相信他將會發生意外」
He says, " I believe this boy's about to have himself an accident."

1619
02:04:59,603 --> 02:05:02,470
我們跟他熟的老是談起安迪
Those of us who knew him best talk about him often.

1620
02:05:03,140 --> 02:05:04,835
我發誓，他總是帶來話題
I swear, the stuff he pulled...

1621
02:05:05,042 --> 02:05:08,012
「我的朋友可以要兩瓶啤酒」
"My friends could use a couple of beers."

1622
02:05:08,345 --> 02:05:10,006
他成功了
And he got it!

1623
02:05:11,249 --> 02:05:13,648
有時那令我傷心，雖然……
Sometimes it makes me sad, though...

1624
02:05:13,917 --> 02:05:15,350
安迪已經離開了
... Andy being gone.

1625
02:05:16,054 --> 02:05:20,183
我不得不提醒自己有些鳥是不能關在籠子堛
I have to remind myself that some birds aren't meant to be caged.

1626
02:05:20,656 --> 02:05:22,716
它們的羽毛太光亮
Their feathers are just too bright.

1627
02:05:24,429 --> 02:05:26,156
當它們飛走的時候
And when they fly away...

1628
02:05:26,598 --> 02:05:31,000
你會覺得把它們關起來是種罪惡
... the part of you that knows it was a sin to lock them up does rejoice.

1629
02:05:32,070 --> 02:05:33,331
但是
But still...

1630
02:05:33,804 --> 02:05:38,138
它們的離開讓你生活的地方空蕩蕩的
... the place you live in is that much more drab and empty that they're gone.

1631
02:05:42,347 --> 02:05:44,713
可能我只是想念我的朋友了
I guess I just miss my friend.

1632
02:06:09,406 --> 02:06:10,339
請坐
Please sit down.

1633
02:06:16,179 --> 02:06:17,737
瑞德
Ellis Boyd Redding...

1634
02:06:18,281 --> 02:06:21,548
你因終身監禁已被關了40年了
...your files say you've served 40 years of a life sentence.

1635
02:06:22,353 --> 02:06:24,479
你覺得你已改過了嗎？
You feel you've been rehabilitated?

1636
02:06:26,357 --> 02:06:27,915
改過？
Rehabilitated?

1637
02:06:29,960 --> 02:06:31,861
讓我想想
Well, now, let me see.

1638
02:06:32,863 --> 02:06:35,196
我不明白那是什麼意思
I don't have any idea what that means.

1639
02:06:37,301 --> 02:06:39,566
你有心理準備重新投入社會嗎？
It means you're ready to rejoin society...

1640
02:06:40,138 --> 02:06:42,469
我知道你們是怎麼想的，老弟
I know what you think it means, sonny.

1641
02:06:44,642 --> 02:06:46,633
對我來說那只是個用來掩飾的詞
To me it's just a made-up word.

1642
02:06:47,978 --> 02:06:50,311
政客用的詞語
A politician's word so that...

1643
02:06:50,747 --> 02:06:54,274
讓你們年青人能穿西裝打領帶
...young fellas like yourself can wear a suit and a tie...

1644
02:06:54,751 --> 02:06:56,344
有一份好工作
...and have a job.

1645
02:06:58,322 --> 02:07:00,415
你倒底想知道些什麼？
What do you really want to know?

1646
02:07:01,192 --> 02:07:03,160
我對自己所犯的罪感到後悔嗎？
Am I sorry for what I did?

1647
02:07:03,394 --> 02:07:04,554
你有後悔嗎？
Well, are you?

1648
02:07:06,464 --> 02:07:09,296
沒有一天我不感到後悔的
There's not a day goes by I don't feel regret.

1649
02:07:10,667 --> 02:07:14,126
不是因為我在監獄堙A或者你認為我該這樣
Not because I'm in here or because you think I should.

1650
02:07:17,608 --> 02:07:20,169
我回首過往
I look back on the way I was then...

1651
02:07:22,313 --> 02:07:23,473
一個年青的……
...a young...

1652
02:07:24,581 --> 02:07:28,073
愚蠢的孩子犯了大罪
...stupid kid who committed that terrible crime.

1653
02:07:31,089 --> 02:07:32,783
我想和他談談
I want to talk to him.

1654
02:07:34,725 --> 02:07:37,193
我想和他講講道理
I want to try and talk some sense to him.

1655
02:07:37,929 --> 02:07:39,863
告訴他做人道理
Tell him the way things are.

1656
02:07:41,965 --> 02:07:43,398
但已經不能了
But I can't.

1657
02:07:45,603 --> 02:07:47,594
那孩子已無影無蹤
That kid's long gone...

1658
02:07:48,805 --> 02:07:51,569
只剩下這個老人
...and this old man is all that's left.

1659
02:07:52,976 --> 02:07:54,443
我得這樣生活下去
I got to live with that.

1660
02:07:55,813 --> 02:07:57,507
改過？
Rehabilitated?

1661
02:07:57,881 --> 02:07:59,712
只是個狗屁的字眼
It's just a bullshit word.

1662
02:08:00,652 --> 02:08:05,419
你繼續蓋上你的印章吧，老弟，別再浪費我的時間了
So you go on and stamp your forms, sonny, and stop wasting my time.

1663
02:08:06,657 --> 02:08:08,921
說句實話
Because to tell you the truth...

1664
02:08:09,260 --> 02:08:11,251
我根本不在乎
...I don't give a shit.

1665
02:08:24,360 --> 02:08:25,651
「通過」

1666
02:09:21,382 --> 02:09:23,347
「布魯斯到此」

1667
02:09:37,782 --> 02:09:39,180
你的，小姐
Here you go, miss.

1668
02:09:42,120 --> 02:09:43,144
我可以去洗手間嗎？
Restroom break?

1669
02:09:48,960 --> 02:09:53,488
你不用每次都問我，去吧
You don't need to ask me every time you need to go take a piss. Just go.

1670
02:10:06,544 --> 02:10:09,604
四十年來我小便都要經過批准
Forty years I've been asking permission to piss.

1671
02:10:10,447 --> 02:10:13,439
不批准的話一滴都尿不出來
I can't squeeze a drop without say-so.

1672
02:10:16,953 --> 02:10:19,114
現實是很難面對的
There's a harsh truth to face.

1673
02:10:20,791 --> 02:10:23,693
我不習慣外面的生活
No way I'm going to make it on the outside.

1674
02:10:31,568 --> 02:10:35,264
我總在想怎樣才能違反假釋條例
All I do anymore is think of ways to break my parole...

1675
02:10:36,073 --> 02:10:38,541
那樣他們會把我再送進去
... so maybe they'd send me back.

1676
02:10:43,747 --> 02:10:46,181
生活在恐懼中是很可怕的
Terrible thing, to live in fear.

1677
02:10:47,085 --> 02:10:48,746
布魯克是知道的
Brooks Hatlen knew it.

1678
02:10:48,952 --> 02:10:50,886
他知道得太清楚了
Knew it all too well.

1679
02:10:52,489 --> 02:10:55,889
我只想回到能適合我的地方
All I want is to be back where things make sense.

1680
02:10:56,327 --> 02:10:59,056
令我不用再擔心受怕的地方
Where I won't have to be afraid all the time.

1681
02:11:01,064 --> 02:11:03,430
只有一件事阻止了我這麼做
Only one thing stops me.

1682
02:11:04,868 --> 02:11:07,269
我對安迪作出的承諾
A promise I made to Andy.

1683
02:11:27,791 --> 02:11:28,917
就在那
There it is.

1684
02:11:39,537 --> 02:11:41,197
非常感謝，先生
Much obliged, sir.

1685
02:11:51,082 --> 02:11:52,347
「布克斯頓」

1686
02:15:20,523 --> 02:15:21,786
親愛的瑞德
Dear Red:

1687
02:15:22,025 --> 02:15:24,493
若你能看到這封信，那你已經出來了
If you're reading this, you've gotten out...

1688
02:15:24,694 --> 02:15:28,755
……如果你已來了這麼遠，也許可以再前進一點
... and if you've come this far, maybe you'd come a bit further.

1689
02:15:29,032 --> 02:15:31,501
你還記得那個地方的名字，是嗎？
You remember the name of the town, don't you?

1690
02:15:33,804 --> 02:15:35,294
聖哈塔尼奧
Zihuatanejo.

1691
02:15:36,940 --> 02:15:40,536
我需要一個人和我一起工作
I could use a good man to help me get my project on wheels.

1692
02:15:41,045 --> 02:15:44,572
我期待你的到來，計劃已經擺好了
I'll keep an eye out for you, and the chessboard ready.

1693
02:15:45,382 --> 02:15:46,782
記住，瑞德
Remember, Red...

1694
02:15:47,117 --> 02:15:49,211
有希望是件好事情
... hope is a good thing...

1695
02:15:49,420 --> 02:15:51,411
也許是世間最好的事情
... maybe the best of things.

1696
02:15:51,621 --> 02:15:53,782
好的事情從不會逝去
And no good thing ever dies.

1697
02:15:54,324 --> 02:15:57,192
我希望這封信能見到你
I will be hoping that this letter finds you...

1698
02:15:57,394 --> 02:15:59,123
見到你很好
... and finds you well.

1699
02:15:59,630 --> 02:16:00,858
你的朋友
Your friend...

1700
02:16:01,064 --> 02:16:02,224
安迪
... Andy.

1701
02:16:36,066 --> 02:16:37,795
「要麼忙著活」
"Get busy living...

1702
02:16:38,002 --> 02:16:39,901
「要麼忙著死」
... or get busy dying. "

1703
02:16:42,605 --> 02:16:44,766
這話一點都沒錯
That's goddamn right.

1704
02:16:47,445 --> 02:16:49,748
「瑞德也來過」

1705
02:16:50,012 --> 02:16:52,139
我一生中第二次……
For the second time in my life...

1706
02:16:52,383 --> 02:16:54,941
犯了罪
... I'm guilty of committing a crime.

1707
02:16:56,020 --> 02:16:57,954
違反了假釋條例
Parole violation.

1708
02:16:58,620 --> 02:17:02,284
當然，我懷疑他們會因此設下路障
Of course I doubt they'll toss up any roadblocks for that.

1709
02:17:02,959 --> 02:17:04,985
尤其是像我這樣的老人家
Not for an old crook like me.

1710
02:17:05,196 --> 02:17:07,221
德薩斯州，漢格堡
Fort Hancock, Texas, please.

1711
02:17:10,900 --> 02:17:15,633
我發現我很激動，幾乎坐不住，思緒紛亂
I find I'm so excited I can barely sit still or hold a thought in my head.

1712
02:17:16,073 --> 02:17:19,405
這是一個自由人才能感受到的
I think it's the excitement only a free man can feel.

1713
02:17:19,610 --> 02:17:22,100
一個自由人開始了漫長的旅程
A free man at the start of a long journey...

1714
02:17:22,312 --> 02:17:24,905
伴隨著未知的結局
... whose conclusion is uncertain.

1715
02:17:27,918 --> 02:17:30,579
我希望我能成功越過邊界
I hope I can make it across the border.

1716
02:17:32,088 --> 02:17:35,114
我希望看見我的朋友，和他握手
I hope to see my friend and shake his hand.

1717
02:17:36,993 --> 02:17:41,054
我希望太平洋的海水如我夢中那樣的藍
I hope the Pacific is as blue as it has been in my dreams.

1718
02:17:42,982 --> 02:17:44,108
我希望……
I hope.

1719
02:18:18,636 --> 02:18:23,539
「謹此紀念亞倫格林」

1720
02:18:26,778 --> 02:18:31,477
劇終 謝謝收看

1721
02:18:32,778 --> 02:18:41,477
